doc.after: The autopatrolled formerly autoreviewer user right is intended to reduce the workload of new page patrollers and causes articles created by autopatrolled users to be automatically marked as patrolled It means that the user can be trusted not to submit inappropriate material deliberately or otherwise and that the user submits new material often enough that it is more efficient to mark it all as approved preemptively
